pis: pis (Slackware Post-Install Scripts)
pis:      
pis: Slackware Post-Instalation Scripts (PIS) are a set of shell scripts for
pis: automating the most tedious Slackware version 15.0 post-installation 
pis: configuration tasks.
pis: 
pis:         'Let the Slackers be a little bit lazy. ;)'
